         <abstract id="aspace_e644c93c6747fae47e76c8d05f5cea0a">The papers contain correspondence, notes, and reports on politics in Connecticut and New Hampshire during the Reconstruction Era, forestry and timber lands, and Yale alumni activities in Washington, D.C., plus a small collection of autograph letters and clipped signatures.</abstract>
